oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Williamson Street in Milan, Tennessee
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Black and white photograph of Williamson Street in Milan, Tennessee. Shown is the Ritz Theater on the right, Frank's Market, a shoe store, Martin's Department Store, Philco and Casey's Department Store. There is snow on the ground from a storm that brought 18 inches of snow.
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:source: Looking Back at Tennessee Photograph Collection, 1890-1981
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Snow; Automobiles; Stores & shops; People
